TODO: replace with a real 512x512 PNG export of icon.svg.

This placeholder text file is committed so the manifest path resolves during
build. To generate the real PNG, run something like:

  rsvg-convert -w 512 -h 512 web/public/icons/icon.svg \
    > web/public/icons/icon-512.png

or use any SVG-to-PNG tool of your choice.
